&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;No development relating to the removal or alterations of the main roof shall take place until:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;(a) at least two activity bat surveys are undertaken in accordance with the&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;Preliminary Ecological Appraisal (7 October 2024) have been
completed and submitted to the Local Planning Authority for conditional approval; or&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;(b) if&amp;nbsp; bats are found and any 
discrepancies between the two surveys,&amp;nbsp; a third survey is submitted to fully&amp;nbsp;characterise the roost. The results of the surveys (if bats are present) will inform an appropriate mitigation/compensation strategy that will ensure that bats are safe guarded during works and that bats are maintained at a favourable conservation status locally. These results are to be submitted to the Local Planning Authority for approval.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

